0228cd2e-3a93-44b9-8378-9374e80dc7b9.title: Haris
0228cd2e-3a93-44b9-8378-9374e80dc7b9.text:
Come now Effendi, to pass you must tell me a story,
one of grand heroics!

39466d25-ddfe-4985-969e-8424b7bed80a.text:
You tell the tale of how you bested a goblin, it lacks heroics and
sounds more like senseless murder.

01621918-2d48-42a2-9b14-a6912598bf12.title: <player>
01621918-2d48-42a2-9b14-a6912598bf12.text:
...And then I pulled the goblin mail from the corpse, but
it didn't fit, so I dropped it.

57701f67-4c98-4392-ba7e-d2d45dbeb2fa.title: Haris
57701f67-4c98-4392-ba7e-d2d45dbeb2fa.text:
You thought that was a story of heroics?! Come back
when you have something worth telling.

9532a347-c367-486b-8d58-b97d5a3b0083.text:
To gain entrance to the resource area, you must first complete the
Dragon Slayer I quest.

dccea161-3dc0-4c04-950c-b8a321cb215c.title: Haris
dccea161-3dc0-4c04-950c-b8a321cb215c.text:
Me? I am Haris! Owner of the area north of here, it
has great resources, I assure you.

d0a1fd61-f391-42df-a9d1-06dfdd290575.title: <player>
d0a1fd61-f391-42df-a9d1-06dfdd290575.text: You own the land? Who did you buy it from?

b9108e46-cd9e-46e8-bd46-a691b101d7f7.title: Haris
b9108e46-cd9e-46e8-bd46-a691b101d7f7.text: Buy? Oh no no no. Do you see this sword, Effendi?

edd2060d-acc7-4955-b195-2552cea74c88.title: Haris
edd2060d-acc7-4955-b195-2552cea74c88.text: Well then, that is why it is mine! Hahaha.

1eb4490b-7d90-49ad-b715-bae932ae2579.title: <player>
1eb4490b-7d90-49ad-b715-bae932ae2579.text: Oh, so do I pay a toll? 10 coins should do, right?

79af4ca5-ee68-452c-afe3-e1ba97c7d0f0.title: Haris
79af4ca5-ee68-452c-afe3-e1ba97c7d0f0.text:
Not quite, while gold can get you many places, I seek
stories of heroics, for my land is only for the worthy.

f004f423-87a1-4189-9bb2-3abc9565ec55.title: <player>
f004f423-87a1-4189-9bb2-3abc9565ec55.text: Is the story behind your sword one of heroics?

6f7c364a-56b7-4fdb-b76e-3d06f4edef3d.title: Haris
6f7c364a-56b7-4fdb-b76e-3d06f4edef3d.text:
I promise you, the monkey I took it from was big!
Hahaha!
